{
  "id": "adv_card_kor_08_03",
  "title": "fran",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――舞台初日",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "『ふはははは、今更来ても遅いぞ、プカミ達』\n『皆が病で苦しむのを、黙って見ているがいい！』",
      "startTime": 7.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "『な……なんだと！？　ワクチン……』\n『病に立ち向かう力を与えるアイテムだと……？』",
      "startTime": 16.3999981563,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "『おのれ、おのれ、ポンピピン！』\n『くっ、あの時、逃がさずにさえおれば……！！』",
      "startTime": 24.6666648229,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cheers-in-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4833.335177100001,
          "startTime": 29.5
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "『きゃああああーーーー！！』",
      "startTime": 28.6761662961,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 32.6062364341
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（凄いな、小さな子から大人まで大盛り上がりだ）\n（稽古中は本当に、どうなることかと思ったけど……）",
      "startTime": 39.1333331426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_festivalstage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "festivalstage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.1333331426
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.3382314445
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 44.3382314445
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "…………え？\n基本的に、私の演技プランで進めていい……ですか？",
      "startTime": 46.4715329887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 51.3047393561
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "それは、ありがとうございます\nでも、方針転換した理由をお聞かせいただいても？",
      "startTime": 54.3333331426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（嘘だろ、優にはあんなに厳しかった蟻田さんが）\n（franさんには、あちらから折れた！？）",
      "startTime": 62.0333331426,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 64.97746106
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "ふんふん。……他人の意見に耳を傾けようともせず\n自分の考えを押し通そうとするのは、どうかと思うけど",
      "startTime": 70.2999998093,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor008.m4a",
      "text": "部下の忠告を聞かずに、結局やられてばかりの\nネクロの姿そのものでもある……ですか",
      "startTime": 77.4000018438,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 82.0527237973
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor009.m4a",
      "text": "私の演技に矯正したいところは山ほどあるけど\nせっかくのネクロらしさを削るのも残念だから",
      "startTime": 85.4333351771,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor010.m4a",
      "text": "今回だけは例外で、意見を通すことにしたと",
      "startTime": 89.0155809166,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（つまり、franさんの態度が悪役っぽいから）\n（舞台でもそのままのキャラでいくってことか……？）",
      "startTime": 97.7333412806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_vanstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "vanstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.3826842866
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor011.m4a",
      "text": "ふふふ、なるほど。それでは、ご期待にお応えしまして\n本番では、もっとネクロになりきってみせますよ！",
      "startTime": 108.1333412806,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "（褒められてるのかどうかはよく分からないけど……）\n（……まぁ、franさんが納得してるならいいか）",
      "startTime": 116.5371800501,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――舞台の閉幕後",
      "startTime": 121.3555163624,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4477.823074400007,
          "startTime": 125.8333394368
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_office-01-evening.webp",
      "bgName": "env_adv_3d_office-01-000-evening",
      "startTime": 122.4555153452
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor012.m4a",
      "text": "ふふ……あー、私ってばなんでも出来ちゃうのよね\nああ、自分の才能が怖いわ……",
      "startTime": 129.2666720708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "franさん、なんだか嬉しそうですね\n何か、いいニュースでもありましたか？",
      "startTime": 136.0000054042,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor013.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、『ぷりエン』の舞台の講評が上がってたんです\n演劇の評論家だか、結構偉い人が書いたみたいですけど",
      "startTime": 143.1666720708,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor014.m4a",
      "text": "好評だった第一弾を踏まえての次回作は\n往々にして高まった期待を超えられないものだが……",
      "startTime": 151.1333163578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor015.m4a",
      "text": "今作はその不安を払拭し、さらなる広がりを見せた\nそれは敵側のドラマもきちんと描いたことにより……",
      "startTime": 160.0333163578,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor016.m4a",
      "text": "ね？　私のこと、べた褒めじゃないです？",
      "startTime": 164.8529075547,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "ええ。俺から見ても、いい舞台でしたよ",
      "startTime": 168.9335423076,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "でも稽古の最終日まで、蟻田さんと言い合ってたので\n見守るこっちは気が気じゃなかったですけどね……",
      "startTime": 177.0666496912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor017.m4a",
      "text": "あれはクリエイター同士のぶつかり合いってやつですよ\nいいものを作るためには、妥協は出来ないんです",
      "startTime": 184.2999830245,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor018.m4a",
      "text": "今思えば、蟻田さんもなんだかんだいい人でしたね\nまた一緒に仕事してもいいかなーってくらいには",
      "startTime": 192.3333153406,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "喉元過ぎればって感じですね\n稽古中は毎日、楽屋で愚痴を言ってたのに",
      "startTime": 199.2333072025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "ただ、トリエル……と言うかすみれが気疲れしてたので\n次があれば、もうちょっと控えめにお願いします……",
      "startTime": 207.9666517257,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor019.m4a",
      "text": "善処しまーす",
      "startTime": 211.955086335,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "あと、そういえば。『ぷりエン』の舞台の運営から\n当初の予定にはなかったお金まで振り込まれてたんです",
      "startTime": 217.6666496912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "その振込の内訳は「ネクログッズのマージン」と\nあったんですが、franさんは何かご存じですか？",
      "startTime": 225.8333122889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor020.m4a",
      "text": "え、ええと……ネクロを演じたのは私なんですから\n私にもマージンが入るのは当然では？",
      "startTime": 236.1666415532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-kor021.m4a",
      "text": "お金くれるなら、もらっとけばいいじゃないですか\nボーナスだ、ラッキーってことで。私もほしいですし",
      "startTime": 242.4333082199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03/sud_vo_adv_card_kor_08_03-koh012.m4a",
      "text": "だとしても、契約はちゃんとしないと後で困りますから\n三枝さんにも伝えて、書面を交わしてもらわないと",
      "startTime": 251.6999738693,
